### Why this matters

Founder direct ratify 2026-06-10 verbatim: "I don't feel like I need to speak to you directly, I need to get Mnemosynec to speak to you — also, because then you can use the same system of Hexadecimal Tags with Socceri to communicate with one another, and no need to change it to human language until she translates. Right? And I want to make all of that, today. Realtime Slipstream Quicksilver. Not your token time."

